---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Subscribe - From The Dumpster Fire" description="Get the week's best finds from across the internet, rescued from the algorithmic chaos.">
  <div class="container">
    <article class="subscribe-page">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>Subscribe</h1>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </header>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="description">
          <p>Every week, you're drowning in content. Algorithms optimized for engagement, not insight. Rage bait, hot takes, and manufactured controversy. The internet wasn't supposed to work this way.</p>

          <p>This newsletter is rescue work. I spend my week diving into the dumpster fire so you don't have to. The good stuff still existsâ€”thoughtful essays, forgotten art, poems that actually say something, ideas worth your time. It's just buried under the noise.</p>

          <p>What you get: Essays that change how you think, not just what you think about. Art and poetry with context that matters. Research that hasn't been flattened into a tweet. Letters from the past that speak to now. Everything curated by a human who reads for understanding, not engagement metrics.</p>

          <p>One email a week. No spam, no tracking, no algorithmic manipulation. Just signal rescued from noise, delivered to your inbox. You can unsubscribe anytime, obviously.</p>

          <p>If you're tired of letting algorithms decide what you read, subscribe below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="form-container">
          <iframe
            src="https://bhuvan.substack.com/embed"
            width="480"
            height="320"
            frameborder="0"
            scrolling="no"
            class="substack-embed"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <p class="fallback-link">
          Form not loading? <a href="https://bhuvan.substack.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe on Substack</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .subscribe-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    position: relative;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 80px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--flame);
    margin: var(--space-md) auto 0;
  }

  .content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .description {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  /* Drop cap on first paragraph */
  .description p:first-of-type::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.85;
    float: left;
    margin: 0.1rem 0.15rem 0 0;
    color: var(--flame);
  }

  .description p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .substack-embed {
    max-width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-whisper);
    background: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .fallback-link {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-medium);
  }

  .fallback-link a {
    color: var(--flame);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--flame);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .fallback-link a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    background: rgba(217, 123, 103, 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .subscribe-page {
      padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .form-container iframe {
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 350px !important;
    }
  }
</style>
